<h1> AIT EVENTS PLAN</h1>

<div class="answer-block">
  <h2> 1(a) </h2>
  <p>
    One of the main things people benefit from is that they get to know about all the activities taking place inside the
    community which is AIT in our case. It also deals with some level of automation wherein people had to previously
    create an even and then send out additional emails related to the event or do it manually by print in bulletin
    boards. For example we can consider a cultural event which is scheduled on a particular date and it requires
    volunteers, this call for volunteers again has to be done separately by email or manually by paper. This process can
    be automated in our system wherein we have an option directly after the creation of an event to call for volunteers.
  </p>
  <h2> 1(b) </h2>
