    <dt>Admin with limited access(SU Committee Heads)</dt>
    <dd>-People who has access to particular group events.</dd>
  </dl>
  <h2> 1(d).</h2>
  <p>
    Ideally a smartphone user must be allowed to create events from his device and also receive notifications about the
    various events taking place.
  </p>
